    <p style="margin-left:40px;"><i>I would like to book an appointment on 28 Oct at 3pm with Denise.</i></p>
    <p style="margin-left:40px;"><i>I would like to cancel my appointment.</i></p>
    <p style="margin-left:40px;"><i>I would like to change my appointment to 4pm instead.</i></p>
    <p style="margin-left:40px;"><i>I would like to check my appointment details.</i></p>
    <br />
    @*<p>And...if I'm not getting you, or you are getting frustrated with me.. I can help you get a <u>human's attention</u> with something similar to the following:</p>

